{"tid":2159767,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"遷台港人首半年增116%","createTime":"2020-08-16T13:42:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-16T13:43:44.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f91ecac20f8981d944ee55df4fc4076edeea3c7a","tid":2159767,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T13:42:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200816/SLQR4VNUHFDQBATKBVTKOLTEQY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200816%2FSLQR4VNUHFDQBATKBVTKOLTEQY%2F&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJEigq9hDTRyGE5nekVWm24Q%3D&h=7a173233\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200816%2FSLQR4VNUHFDQBATKBVTKOLTEQY%2F&h=9d337ec8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200816/SLQR4VNUHFDQBATKBVTKOLTEQY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n遷台港人首半年增116%<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/6IFsdnUv6y62FkXS1JdnPfMPaEY=/5760x3840/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/3T2OCT5UUJHCPPORZJ32I6R2TA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F6IFsdnUv6y62FkXS1JdnPfMPaEY%3D%2F5760x3840%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F3T2OCT5UUJHCPPORZJ32I6R2TA.jpg&h=85cbaf5c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■香港局勢持續動盪，今年頭半年已有3,161人移居台灣。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n香港政治敗壞，一國兩制幾乎蕩然無存，不少港人計劃移民台灣。根據台內政部移民署最新統計，今年1月至6月港人居留許可人數達3,161人，較去年同期1,464人激增116%。<br />\n<br />\n台灣移民署資料統計，自2019年爆發反送中運動後，自9月至12月，香港居民居留許可人數為3,631，全年度高達5,858人，較前年4,148人增加四成，也是移民署自2016年將港。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n預約系統名額排至10月<br />\n<br />\n目前港人可以投資、創業、留學等五種方法申請移居台灣。台駐港辦事處於本周一推出網上預約系統，讓港人預約辦。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n台灣蘋果新聞網昨披露，有在海外運作的系統可查詢全台不動產所有權人資料。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n中央社／台灣《蘋果新聞網》"},{"pid":"d6af9294862598be080b4c1ee092fd003e430d57","tid":2159767,"uid":3967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-16T13:43:44.000Z","msg":"UK&gt;TW<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}